title: 'to truth-seekers : student, scientist, futurist'
pid: 4f82f2a6-ed09-4741-b740-cb1ca0c43abe
body: |2-
  To know everyone, express everything,
  see every (concept) from every (concept),
  see every mind from every other that looked --
  a shared knowledge graph is the only data structure
  that conveniently permits these things.
  The shared knowledge graph is the final frontier.
